, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6228] remove the nana filename string, add some exclusions to gitignore
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6227] replace the regex crate with the fancy-regex crate
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6199] allow uppercase chars to be captured during suppressed input
merelymyself 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6220] made 
``cd``
, 
``cp``
, 
``ls``
, 
``mv``
, 
``open``
 and 
``rm``
 automatically strip ansi codes
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6189] allow 
``-h``
 flags for 
``export``
 subcommands
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6149] adds a 
``config reset``
 command
elferherrera created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6217] sqlite query without collect
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6205] use 
``from table``
 to remove into-db command
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6215] Reduced dev-deps by narrowing 
``rstest``
 features
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6211] Make 
``open``
 test independent of locale
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6210] Patch 
``lscolors``
 to not blink
WindSoilder created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6206] In unix like system, set foreground process while running external command
rgwood created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6204] Faster SQLite reads
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6200] Change 
``query``
 command to 
``query db``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6194] Add $OLDPWD example for cd
Kangaxx-0 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/6187] tweaked how nu identifies custom command
